          <h1 class="jumbotron-heading text-muted">A Little Introduction</h1>
          <p class="lead text-muted">Several years ago I moved 1200 miles from my home of over 15 years to move back to Texas for family matters. I was laid off during that time and started a new career. It was fun for awhile but 7 years later I miss coding as as fortune favors me, I was an accident and have been unable to work for the last several month. I started looking back at my old career and decided I needed to do something about it. I've learned a new language, some of the basics of the frameworks available today, all the great things javascript has become and decided to get back to writing code again. Some of the names have changed but the game is the same.</p>
          <p>That being said some of these examples are old and outdated but the fact these applications I helped design and run are still going with the same old code some 6-10 years later.. </p>
